#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:4
msgid "cmake-modules(7)"
msgstr "cmake-模組(7)"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:6
msgid ""
"The modules listed here are part of the CMake distribution. Projects may "
"provide further modules; their location(s) can be specified in the :variable:"
"`CMAKE_MODULE_PATH` variable."
msgstr ""
"此處列出的模組是 CMake 散佈版的一部分。專案可以提供更多模組；其位置可以在 :"
"variable:`CMAKE_MODULE_PATH` 變數中指定。"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:11
msgid "Utility Modules"
msgstr "工具模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:13
msgid "These modules are loaded using the :command:`include` command."
msgstr "這些模組是使用 :command:`include` 命令載入的。"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:95
msgid "Find Modules"
msgstr "尋找模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:97
msgid ""
"These modules search for third-party software. They are normally called "
"through the :command:`find_package` command."
msgstr ""
"這些模組會搜尋第三方軟體。它們通常是透過 :command:`find_package` 命令呼叫的。"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:252
msgid "Deprecated Modules"
msgstr "已棄用的模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:255
msgid "Deprecated Utility Modules"
msgstr "已棄用的工具模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:280
msgid "Deprecated Find Modules"
msgstr "已棄用的尋找模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:300
msgid "Legacy CPack Modules"
msgstr "舊版 CPack 模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:302
msgid ""
"These modules used to be mistakenly exposed to the user, and have been moved "
"out of user visibility. They are for CPack internal use, and should never be "
"used directly."
msgstr ""
"這些模組過去曾被錯誤地暴露給使用者，現已移出使用者視野。它們僅供 CPack 內部使"
"用，不應直接使用。"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:322
msgid "Miscellaneous Modules"
msgstr "其他模組"

#: ../../../manual/cmake-modules.7.rst:324
msgid ""
"These internal modules are not intended to be included directly in projects:"
msgstr "這些內部模組不應直接在專案中引入："
